        "content": "### Setup Checklist\n\n**1. Service API Key** — In **Extract & Filter**, set your real key.\n**2. Meta Webhook** — App Dashboard → WhatsApp: URL = {n8n}/webhook/whatsapp.\n**3. Tenant** — POST /onboarding/setup with meta_phone_number_id (and ai_system_prompt for Something else).\n**4. Send 3 Buttons** — Set META_ACCESS_TOKEN in n8n env or use Header Auth credential (Bearer token).\n**5. Credentials** — WhatsApp API, Google Gemini.\n\n---\n\n### Flow (templates + one chatbot path)\nFirst message → **Send 3 Buttons**: Order | Products | Something else.\n• **Products** → Get Inventory → **Send Products** (list only).\n• **Order** → Get Inventory → **Format Order Products** → **Send Order Products** (list + add-to-cart CTA). Follow-up: handle reply (e.g. 1x2, 3x1) in another flow → POST /transactions, payment link.\n• **Something else** → **AI Agent** (store-info Q&A only) → Send Reply → Store Outbound.",
